{"about_the_game":"<i>The Deckarium demo lets you play through about 25% of the game.</i><br><br>Deckarium is a deck-building pet simulator. Play pet cards to add to your terrarium or aquarium, and progress through levels to unlock new cards to add to your deck.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/frog.gif?t=1736996847\" /><br><br>Keep your pets well fed and they'll produce coins for you. Some pets have bigger appetites than others! You will have to maintain the food-chain if you want to benefit from larger pets.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/foodchain.gif?t=1736996847\" /><br><br>Your pets aren't the only ones who are hungry! Beware of ghosts who seek only to consume the souls of your pets!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/ghost.gif?t=1736996847\" /><br><br>Beat levels and minigames to earn extra currency for your own personal idle terrarium and vivarium, where you can collect and name your own unique pets without fear of phantoms!<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/extras/snail.gif?t=1736996847\" />","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1736996847","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/page_bg_generated.jpg?t=1736996847","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1736996847","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3019910/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1736996847","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Game demo","id":10}],"content_descriptors":{"ids":[],"notes":null},"detailed